Calvin Klein Guess Women's Kate Spade Kate Spade New York Handbags Michael Kors Michael Kors Handbags Tommy Hilfiger Tommy Hilfiger Women's Women's Sandals Women's Tops



Macy's Home StoreFunctional and fashionable items for the home are just a click away at macys.com. Discover fabulous collections of tableware and dinnerware to enhance your dining and entertaining. From fine china to flatware to casual plates and bowls, finding everything you need is a snap. Before the table is set and the drinks poured, the food has to be prepared—explore the wide selection of kitchen electrics and cookware sets, and make your culinary experience a breeze.
Looking for casual dinnerware for the home? These daily essentials can be mixed and matched with a variety of plates and bowls, giving your table a laid-back style that’s perfect for ordinary days and nights. Got your dishes squared away? Check out the selection of glassware. Whether you’re stocking a home bar or kitchen cabinet, explore the range of mugs, cups and stemware. Sprucing up your collection of fine china? The crisp radiance of bone china is a fabulous choice.
Shopping for flatware and silverware for the home? Go big with a 65-piece set and rest assured that you’ve got every situation covered, from housewarmings to holidays. Of course, when it comes to cooking, a drawer full of butter knives just won’t cut it. Browse the collection of cutlery sets and meet the needs of the household cook. Accessorize with handsome knife blocks and cutting boards that fit into any kitchen counter aesthetic.
Kitchen appliances for the home range from quick-and-easy juicers to professional quality mixers and coffee makers. In the mood for some slow cooking? A crock pot is just the thing. Shop the latest in toaster ovens and find great space-saving ways to keep food hot and crispy. Round out your collection with specialty electrics such as waffle and brownie makers.
Great meals begin with great cookware for the home. Add to your existing collection with stainless steel pots and pans, or opt for a new set of cast-iron dishes. Serve up perfect breakfasts and burgers with handy griddle pans. Add some healthy steamed veggies to your diet with a classic multi-pot. Discover everything you need for hassle-free dining and entertaining at Macy’s. Looking for huge savings? Shop our Black Friday, Cyber Monday and Holiday Gift Guide!












